timing_extrac...sis_in_library(25.10)    timing_extrac...sis_in_library(25.10)

Name
       timing_extract_model_case_analysis_in_library

Syntax
       timing_extract_model_case_analysis_in_library

       {true | false}

       Default: true

       Enables  the  software  to model the constants as a function in the ex-
       tracted timing model.

       When set to true, the software models constants as functions in the li-
       brary if these propagate to the output port.

       When set to false, instead of modeling constants  as  functions  inside
       the  library, these are written as set_case_analysis in the constraints
       file (*.asrt).

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

